snippet.title: Agent Ching Attacks | Official Trailer | Atlee & Ranveer Singh | Sreeleela, Bobby Deol  🔥🔥🔥
snippet.description:
The biggest, spiciest ad film of the year is HERE! 
Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Watch the explosive trailer of AGENT CHING ATTACKS with jaw-dropping action, whistle-worthy drama, foot-tapping music, and masala so hot… it’ll set your screen on fire.

The full film premieres Sunday, October 19 exclusively on this channel.

WHAT TO EXPECT:
• Ranveer Singh in his most powerful avatar yet as Agent Ching
• Sreeleela adding spice and swagger as Agent Mirchi
• Bobby Deol unleashing chaos as Professor White Noise
• Signature Atlee scale, style & spectacle with a global A-list crew
• A brand-new version of the iconic anthem “My Name is Ranveer Ching”

From Bhatinda to Beijing, there’s only one king… Ranveer Ching!

This is the BIGGEST celebration of Desi Chinese ever — bold, flavourful, cinematic, and guaranteed to #AagLagaDe.

About Ching’s Secret - They say that to win Hindustani hearts even Chinese food became desi! And there’s only one Desi Chinese food brand that can make desi hearts beat faster – Ching’s. Saucy. Spicy. Sweet and sour. Hot and sour. Crunchy. Slurpy. Zesty. Schezwani. Manchurian… Whatever be the kind of Desi Chinese your palate craves for, only Ching’s can hit the spot with a perfect zing.

I ♥ Desi Chinese!

snippet.title: Laxmi Aarti | Om Jai Laxmi Mata | Lakshmi Mata Ki Aarti | Laxmi Mata Aarti | Diwali | Dhanteras
snippet.description:
Laxmi Aarti | Om Jai Laxmi Mata | Lakshmi Mata Ki Aarti | Laxmi Mata Aarti | Diwali | Dhanteras

🌸 Om Jai Laxmi Mata 🌸
Listen to this divine Lakshmi Mata Ki Aarti and invite prosperity, peace, and positivity into your home this Diwali and Dhanteras.
Chant with devotion and experience the blessings of Goddess Mahalaxmi, the goddess of wealth and fortune.

✨ Aarti Lyrics (in Hindi):
ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता, मैया जय लक्ष्मी माता।
तुमको निशदिन सेवत, हरि विष्णु विधाता॥

🕯️ Perfect for:

Dhanteras Puja
Diwali Laxmi Pujan
Friday Aarti
Daily Evening Bhakti

Title :- Om Jai Lakshmi Mata 
Singer :- Varsha Shrivastava
Music :- Vijay Nanda
Video :- SMP Studio

अपने दिन को सकारात्मक ऊर्जा से भरने के लिए सब्सक्राइब कीजिये और अपने मित्र परिवार के साथ शेर कीजिये| 
🔔 SUBSCRIBE NOW: 
https://www.youtube.com/@ShemarooBhakti

Top Laxmi Bhajan, Aarti, Gatha

Laxmi Aarti                                                  https://youtu.be/oec7CXRAfeE
Laxmi Aarti by Anuradha Paudwal-          https://youtu.be/zdZ67AM47u8
Mahalakshmi Stotram -                              https://youtu.be/13FH5CEUL4I
Laxmi Pooja Aarti           -                           https://youtu.be/t1S2Z38rfZI
Lakshmi Chalisa by Anuradha Paudwal - https://youtu.be/tNwmNfu-vAc

Lyrics

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता, मैया जय लक्ष्मी माता।
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Maiya Jai Lakshmi Mata.

तुमको निशिदिन सेवत, हरि विष्णु विधाता॥
Tumko Nishidin Sevat, Hari Vishnu Vidhata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

उमा, रमा, ब्रह्माणी, तुम ही जग-माता।
Uma, Rama, Brahmani, Tum Hi Jag-Mata.

सूर्य-चंद्रमा ध्यावत, नारद ऋषि गाता॥
Surya-Chandrama Dhyavat, Narad Rishi Gata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

दुर्गा रुप निरंजनी, सुख सम्पत्ति दाता।
Durga Roop Niranjani, Sukh Sampatti Data.

जो कोई तुमको ध्यावत, ऋद्धि-सिद्धि धन पाता॥
Jo Koi Tumko Dhyavat, Riddhi-Siddhi Dhan Pata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

तुम पाताल-निवासिनि, तुम ही शुभदाता।
Tum Patal-Nivasini, Tum Hi Shubhdata.

कर्म-प्रभाव-प्रकाशिनी, भवनिधि की त्राता॥
Karm-Prabhav-Prakashini, Bhavanidhi Ki Trata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

जिस घर में तुम रहतीं, सब सद्गुण आता।
Jis Ghar Mein Tum Rahti, Sab Sadgun Aata.

सब सम्भव हो जाता, मन नहीं घबराता॥
Sab Sambhav Ho Jata, Man Nahi Ghabrata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

तुम बिन यज्ञ न होते, वस्त्र न कोई पाता।
Tum Bin Yagya Na Hote, Vastra Na Koi Pata.

खान-पान का वैभव, सब तुमसे आता॥
Khan-Pan Ka Vaibhav, Sab Tumse Aata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

शुभ-गुण मंदिर सुंदर, क्षीरोदधि-जाता।
Shubh-Gun Mandir Sundar, Kshirodadhi-Jata.

रत्न चतुर्दश तुम बिन, कोई नहीं पाता॥
Ratna Chaturdash Tum Bin, Koi Nahi Pata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

महालक्ष्मीजी की आरती, जो कोई जन गाता।
Mahalakshmi Ji Ki Aarti, Jo Koi Jan Gata.

उर आनन्द समाता, पाप उतर जाता॥
Ur Anand Samata, Paap Utar Jata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution - Official Teaser Trailer (English Subtitles)
snippet.description:
The best of the Shibuya Incident arc combines with the debut of the first two episodes of Season 3's Culling Game arc in this exclusive theatrical event! Coming to North America exclusively in movie theatres starting December 5.

A veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.
Yuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.
In the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.
The desperate confrontation between Satoru Gojo’s two beloved students comes to the big screen with an early preview. Be the first to experience Yuji and Yuta’s fateful battle with the hotly anticipated kickoff to Season 3 in theatres nationwide.

#IGN #Anime

snippet.title: HALLELUJAH CHALLENGE || OCT 2025 || DAY 12 OVERFLOW
snippet.description: Hallelujah Challenge is an inter-denominational gathering of Christians on virtual platforms led by Pastor Nathaniel Bassey (Nathaniel Bassey). This is done by having worship sessions in music through the HolySpirt/ by the help of the Holy Spirit. Consequently, the performance of songs are spontaneous and performed for strictly non-commercial purposes whether alone by Nathaniel Bassey with the help of his team, or with third parties such as YouTube, Instagram or Facebook. The performance of any song whatsoever in terms of their lyrics, sounds, beats etc is not of a manner as to deprive the owners of such songs of their exclusive rights of ownership. The songs on the Challenge may feature songs owned by Nathaniel Bassey, songs owned by other spirit filled gospel artistes, as well as contemporary Christian music which are performed for religious purposes in churches and other Christian gatherings, which shall be duly acknowledged.  We affirm that the Challenge does not deprive copyright owners of their economic rights, as they are not performed for entertainment or popularity.

snippet.title: Ali Amran feat Melissa Sekhi
snippet.description:
Nouveau single tiré de mon nouvel album à venir :  "Gar Yigenni d tmurt"

"À travers des paroles sobres et poignantes, Ali Amran aborde la fuite des cerveaux et la douleur des générations contraintes de s’exiler pour construire leur avenir. Fidèle à son style mêlant poésie et lucidité, il livre une réflexion profonde sur la condition de la jeunesse et l’absence d’espoir dans certaines régions du pays". Sarali Bellamine (commentaire sur Facebook)

Dihir axir

Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
ṛuḥ a mmi, dihin axir
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-is i ddunit
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir

Ziɣ mačči dayen isehlen
tura mi d-tewweḍ rrekba
xas ẓriɣ dayen ilaqen
ɣer daxel, ččiɣ tiyita
‘g yiwwas ad tṛuḥeḍ dayen
lḥess-ik ur s-selleɣ ara
ma siwleɣ w'ara d-yerren
w'ara d-yinin : aql-i da !

Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
ṛuḥ a mmi dihin axir
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-is i ddunit
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir

'G wasmi telliḍ d ameẓyan
nekki d aḥebbeṛ fell-ak
d ac'ara k-d-aǧwen wussan
m' ara tekfuḍ leqraya-k
tamurt ur tesɛi laman
amek ad tḍemneḍ azekka-k?
asigna s-tekkat yettban

wagi d-yuɣen d asekkak

Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
A lbaz areqman
ṛuḥ a mmi dihin axir
ẓwer kan
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-is i ddunit
abrid ad k-iban
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir
a w’ufan

I yessers deg-neɣ zzman
I nɛebba mebla lebɣi
rwin ula d iḥulfan
ger tasa ‘d wul, d imenɣi
nefṛeḥ nessufeɣ igwerdan
d lxir i sen-nettmenni
ǧǧan-d ilem yesseḥzan
nṛebba-ten i lbeṛṛani

Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
ṛuḥ a mmi dihin axir
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-isi ddunit
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir
Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
A lbaz areqman
ṛuḥ a mmi dihin axir
ẓwer kan

ad s-tafeḍ ixef-is i ddunit
abrid ad k-iban
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
